WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.960 --> 00:00:02.360
Meng Yi, why are you here?

2
00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:04.700
Sit down

3
00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:13.460
It's cold, drink some hot water to warm your stomach, thank you.

4
00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:16.860
Oh yes, brother-in-law

5
00:00:17.280 --> 00:00:20.480
You haven't told me why you're here.

6
00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:22.160
Secretary Huang and I are friends

7
00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:23.240
I'm waiting for him here too

8
00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:24.880
He went out to work.

9
00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:27.060
I'll read a book here

10
00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:30.040
It's a friend, right?

11
00:00:30.040 --> 00:00:30.920
What happened yesterday

12
00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:32.140
Don't be angry either.

13
00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:35.860
My sister and I grew up with my mother

14
00:00:35.960 --> 00:00:38.140
And my mom, she has no culture.

15
00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:39.600
It's all knife mouth tofu heart

16
00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:40.640
Don't take it to heart

17
00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:41.520
Don't be angry.

18
00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:42.780
She is also good for us

19
00:00:43.240 --> 00:00:45.820
Actually, I'm not that angry with your mother

20
00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:47.500
The key is your sister

21
00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:51.300
3 years ago, I went out to start a business alone for her happiness

22
00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:54.260
How much suffering and how many tears

23
00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:56.000
I came back three years later.

24
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.620
I never expected it to be like this now

25
00:00:58.840 --> 00:01:01.200
I don't think it's possible for me and your sister

